{"tid":2217295,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"日本執政黨保守派議員：邀習近平訪日將貽笑大方","createTime":"2020-09-25T10:22:32.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-25T10:26:26.000Z","uid":75656,"like":14,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"04f1fd0197274bb3c4ac7859b47da42bac23286a","tid":2217295,"uid":75656,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-25T10:22:32.000Z","msg":"日本執政自由民主黨保守派國會議員組成的「保守團結之會」24日做出決議文，要求日本政府取消邀請中國國家主席習近平以國賓身分訪問日本。<br />\n<br />\n日本時事通信社報導，自民黨的保守團結之會(代表召集人為眾議員城內實)24日擬定一份要求政府取消邀請習近平以國賓身分訪日的決議文，預定今天(25日)提交給日本政府。<br />\n<br />\n鑑於中國公務船頻頻航行在釣魚台列嶼(日本稱尖閣諸島)周邊海域，決議文寫道：「對我國安全保障的威脅日趨嚴重。」<br />\n<br />\n決議文還指出，習近平應該為俗稱武漢肺炎的2019年冠狀病毒疾病(COVID-19)疫情蔓延負起責任。<br />\n<br />\n文中寫道：「若邀請習近平以國賓身分訪日，勢必會貽笑大方，應正式取消邀請。」<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.rti.org.tw/news/view/id/2080448\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.rti.org.tw%2Fnews%2Fview%2Fid%2F2080448&d=awVbgeYyyy76%2F43Y8QfwztfEBUFsnbtb5M0%2Bd5EIgxU%3D&h=c7855b5a\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.rti.org.tw/news/view/id/2080448</a>"},{"pid":"8344857d13e0eaaa3aaba2b0a88870c82eb780e4","tid":2217295,"uid":214173,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-25T10:26:18.000Z","msg":"等睇石頭腳<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/peanut.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fd6ba7d49309f27577bc2dc0ceac28ae4de33075","tid":2217295,"uid":115847,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-25T10:26:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://media.giphy.com/media/GpyS1lJXJYupG/giphy.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmedia.giphy.com%2Fmedia%2FGpyS1lJXJYupG%2Fgiphy.gif&h=36a436f5&s={SIZE}\" />"}]}